{
  "stem": "9995.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- in the beginning, we were still not as bad off as some people who had only money and abandoned businesses, which were taken away, and then they had absolutely nothing to live on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not clear in terms of the type of work your mother did before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first, she was in a very big Swedish firm, [NON-ENGLISH], and she was an accountant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was in charge of the whole department.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She also was-- but that was not her main job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was also a very good steno and typist in two languages, Polish and German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the firm [NON-ENGLISH] moved to Warsaw, and we couldn't move because father's job was not in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and besides, the whole family was in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my mother got a different job in this [NON-ENGLISH], which had a branch in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a fairly good job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Besides this, she was an administering several houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she by herself has very good income.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our school had a beautiful camp that was a governmental one in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you apply, and you are a good student, you could go over there because it was very nice and very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, my mother had her vacation-- because the high season was in summertime, she had it at winter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at winter we had, of course, during Christmas, right here, 10 days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had permission to stay three weeks skiing with my mother in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at summertime, I was going to camp for the whole vacation, since I went to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because of this, also, I became very close to some of the girls in my class because we shared experiences together.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
